channel.title: Comments on: Star Warrrs, Nothing but Star Warrrs

item.title: By: Side-Effect
item.dc:creator: Side-Effect
item.description:
Hey dude, makes sense for you to prepay a game, you get one that way, stores only get like 40-60 copies release date. Thats not a lot of copies. Movie theatres sit well over that PER SHOWING.
I dont goto opening nights, ESPECIALLY Lord of the rings or star wars openings... i dont feel like wasting $2000 on ebay to buy a stormtrooper uniform to blend in... after all i dont wanna look like the idiot standing out ;)
